    <item>
      <title>财政部长贝森特将在国会山会见伊丽莎白·沃伦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/treasury-pick-bessent-to-meet-elizabeth-warren-on-capitol-hill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的财政部长斯科特·贝森特将于周三会见经常批评华尔街的民主党参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦，这是他下个月任命听证会之前在国会山举行的一系列会议的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/treasury-pick-bessent-to-meet-elizabeth-warren-on-capitol-hill</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼央行配合企业社会责任基金腐败调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indonesia-central-bank-cooperates-with-graft-probe-of-csr-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚银行行长佩里·瓦吉约 (Perry Warjiyo) 誓言配合央行的腐败调查，本周早些时候，该银行遭到该国反腐败机构的突击搜查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/indonesia-central-bank-cooperates-with-graft-probe-of-csr-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 09:27:38 GMT</pubDate>
