    <item>
      <title>阿萨德政权倒台后叙利亚机场首次恢复航班</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/syria-s-airports-restart-flights-for-first-time-since-assad-fall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴沙尔·阿萨德政权垮台后，叙利亚主要机场首次恢复运营，让这个饱受战争蹂躏的国家恢复了正常状态。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/syria-s-airports-restart-flights-for-first-time-since-assad-fall</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 08:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠誉下调罗马尼亚信用展望，警告预算修复延迟</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/fitch-cuts-romania-credit-outlook-and-warns-of-budget-fix-delay</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级暗示可能下调罗马尼亚的信用评级，理由是该国政治不确定性较高，可能会导致在明年总统重新选举之前削减欧盟最高预算赤字的计划被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/fitch-cuts-romania-credit-outlook-and-warns-of-budget-fix-delay</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 08:35:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟与南美贸易协定为何终将达成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/eu-mercosur-trade-deal-what-does-the-europe-south-america-agreement-involve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟和南美国家花了超过四分之一世纪的时间试图达成自由贸易协议。今年，随着世界最大贸易伙伴——美国和中国——之间即将爆发的贸易战，谈判变得更加紧迫，这促使其他地区寻求新的商业伙伴关系以减轻打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/eu-mercosur-trade-deal-what-does-the-europe-south-america-agreement-involve</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 07:30:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯逮捕杀害将军嫌疑人，指责乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/russia-arrests-suspect-in-killing-of-top-general-blames-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯当局拘留了一名乌兹别克斯坦国民，涉嫌在莫斯科炸弹袭击中杀害一名高级将领，并称他已被乌克兰安全部门招募执行暗杀任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/russia-arrests-suspect-in-killing-of-top-general-blames-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 06:53:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国央行行长李承晚预计戒严令动乱将损害经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bok-s-rhee-expects-martial-law-turmoil-to-hurt-economic-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国央行行长李昌镕周三表示，韩国持续的政治动荡对经济造成压力，暗示当局可能下调增长预测并采取稳定措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/bok-s-rhee-expects-martial-law-turmoil-to-hurt-economic-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 06:25:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国嫌疑人尹某逃避审讯，被捕风险增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-adding-to-risk-of-arrest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，韩国弹劾总统尹锡烈周三未接受联合调查组的询问，这增加了他被捕的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/south-korea-s-yoon-skips-questioning-adding-to-risk-of-arrest</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 01:48:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法拉奇在海湖庄园会晤后表示，马斯克有机会提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/elon-musk-in-talks-to-donate-to-reform-uk-nigel-farage-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民粹主义改革英国党领袖奈杰尔·法拉奇表示，他正在与埃隆·马斯克就政治捐款进行“持续谈判”，这是两人潜在合作的最新迹象，可能威胁英国政坛传统的两党垄断格局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/elon-musk-in-talks-to-donate-to-reform-uk-nigel-farage-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 23:04:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国大臣呼吁反对加强对华商业限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-minister-recently-lobbied-against-tough-china-business-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政部一名大臣游说前保守党政府，要求金融业放松对中国商业活动的限制，凸显出基尔·史塔默政府在新的间谍丑闻爆发期间支持与北京保持联系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-minister-recently-lobbied-against-tough-china-business-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 20:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
